# What motivated Russia to make these unsubstantiated claims?

## Summary
The unsubstantiated claims made by Russia regarding Ukraine's alleged plans to use a "dirty bomb" appear to be motivated by Moscow's desire to discredit Kyiv and to justify its own aggressive actions against its neighbor. These claims have been strongly refuted by Ukraine, the US, the UK and the EU, which have accused Moscow of attempting to launch its own false-flag operation.

